text: Patrick Beaudouin (born 7 April 1953) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Val-de-Marne department, and is a member of the Union for a Popular Movement. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:People from Eure Category:Rally for the Republic politicians Category:The Republicans (France) politicians Category:The Popular Right Category:Mayors of places in Île-de-France Category:Politicians from Île-de-France Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
